metadata.name: DREAMING
metadata.description:
…This is a great state of mind…  
Looks like u fell asleep but with open eyes. U are in your personal beautiful dreamland. The visions, the thoughts are appearing in your head and in front of your eyes. 
Allow yourself to dream big and enjoy this moment.

Photo was taken by Masha Kozhdan. Minsk, May 2021.

Model Liza Belaya (@_liza_belaya)  
Style Alena Fedarovich (@ohmyalena)  
Photographer’s assistant Yuliya Herasimenia (@graphic_design_jg)
